    <briefdescription>
<para>Unlike the classic mesh that stores coordinates of its vertices, this class stores the lengths of all edges. It can be used for construction of intrinsic Intrinsic Delaunay Triangulations. Generated from class <computeroutput><ref refid="classMR_1_1EdgeLengthMesh" kindref="compound">MR.EdgeLengthMesh</ref></computeroutput>. This is the non-const half of the class. </para>
    </briefdescription>
